Every she breaks up with him, he learns from his mistakes, sort of like the movie "Groundhog Day."  He slowly figured out all the things she likes and dislikes as well as her red-flags.   He's been trying to change himself to be the perfect man for her. 

After many unsuccessful attempts, changing his appearance every time, he finally figured out all of the right combinations of personality it took to win her heart.  They eventually became engaged to be married.
